[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Oracle:**                                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m AND 1337=(CASE WHEN (1=1) THEN DBMS_PIPE.RECEIVE_MESSAGE('RANDSTR',10) ELSE  [34m│[0m
